snippet.title: Soft Drizzle - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Soft Drizzle is a short, 64x64 resolution visual novel about friendship and rainy days, made in 7 days for LOWREZJAM 2020. 

Play it at https://lartu.itch.io/soft-drizzle!
